Answer.comment: "I'm not sure whether I remember the name correctly! It was a three letter name, and it was male, but that's all I remember. But I can tell you that he has purple hair, that he likes to visit friends on Sundays, that two of his friends have glasses and one has a hat, and that he can only say one word to communicate with me and that word is \"glasses.\""
Answer.about: "Whether a descriptor is more likely to refer to something that can only be described that way or something that can also be described a different way."
